title: Hour 2 - Chris Russo, Roger Bennett

description:
MLB insider Chris Russo stops by to preview the MLB Divisional Round. And co-host of 'Men in Blazers' Roger Bennett breaks down action from across the pond, including Champions League and World Cup previews.
